{"id": "17323", "revid": "265602", "url": "https://baldursgate.fandom.com/wiki?curid=17323", "title": "Zaviak's Vision Quest", "text": "&lt;a href=\"Zaviak\"&gt;Zaviak&lt;/a&gt;'s Vision is in \"\".\nAcquisition.\nTalk to &lt;a href=\"Zaviak\"&gt;Zaviak&lt;/a&gt; in &lt;a href=\"Elfsong%20Tavern%20%28SoD%29\"&gt;Elfsong Tavern&lt;/a&gt; in and you'll receive a pair of\u00a0&lt;a href=\"Spectacles%20of%20Spectacle\"&gt;Spectacles of Spectacle&lt;/a&gt;.\nWalkthrough.\nWhile any character is wearing the spectacles, occasionally vaguely humanoid white cloud will be seen moving around certain maps. If the wearing character then uses the spectacles on the cloud, it will consume a charge and \"pull\" them to the\u00a0Prime Material Plane.\nThe item begins with 3 charges and is non-rechargeable, but there are a total of 9 encounters where it can be used, requiring a choice as to where they are to be used. Saving beforehand is recommended."}
