{"id": "39427", "revid": "35642161", "url": "https://baldursgate.fandom.com/wiki?curid=39427", "title": "Check the Bodies", "text": "Check the Bodies (CtB) is a mega-mod for &lt;a href=\"Baldur%27s%20Gate%20II\"&gt;Shadows of Amn&lt;/a&gt; that adds the city of Hlondeth, as well as many other unrelated locations and quests in &lt;a href=\"Amn\"&gt;Amn&lt;/a&gt;. In addition, it adds stores, spells, and new items to the game.\nQuests Overview.\nThere are other quests and content available in the full Mod installation as well, which as of Version 3.0 is advertised as A Spellhold Studios mod for Baldur's Gate II, , Baldur's Gate Trilogy, Baldur's Gate II: Enhanced Edition and EET.\nMod Pages.\nSome quests add areas to the game that are outside of the BG2 worldmap limits in the original game and therefore the mod needs the &lt;a href=\"https%3A//github.com/SpellholdStudios/BP-BGT-Worldmap\"&gt;Big World Worldmap mod&lt;/a&gt; installed afterwards on almost all game variants. However, from v3.0 onwards, this mod is compatible with the EET's included worldmap."}
