yr\"&gt;Cordyr&lt;/a&gt;, depends again on the &lt;a href=\"party\"&gt;party&lt;/a&gt;'s &lt;a href=\"reputation\"&gt;reputation&lt;/a&gt; when turning the quest in and on the game's edition:"}
