{"id": "4838", "revid": "265731", "url": "https://baldursgate.fandom.com/wiki?curid=4838", "title": "Crimson Chain", "text": "The Crimson Chain is enchanted chain mail +5. It offers an &lt;a href=\"Armor%20Class\"&gt;Armor Class&lt;/a&gt; of 0. It has the same protection modifiers as normal &lt;a href=\"Chain%20Mail\"&gt;chain mail&lt;/a&gt;. It offers the highest AC for chain mail in the game. It is available exclusively from &lt;a href=\"Ribald%20Barterman%23Special%20Items%20Store\"&gt;Ribald Barterman&lt;/a&gt;."}
