{"id": "8939", "revid": "47673695", "url": "https://baldursgate.fandom.com/wiki?curid=8939", "title": "Edwin's Documents", "text": "Edwin's Documents are a quest item which can be received from the merchant &lt;a href=\"Marcus\"&gt;Marcus&lt;/a&gt; during the stronghold quest &lt;a href=\"Find%20Proof%20of%20Mae%27Var%27s%20Treachery\"&gt;Find Proof of Mae'Var's Treachery&lt;/a&gt;. Marcus is found on the first floor of the &lt;a href=\"Sea%27s%20Bounty%20Tavern\"&gt;Sea's Bounty Tavern&lt;/a&gt; once the task is given to you by &lt;a href=\"Edwin%20Odesseiron\"&gt;Edwin&lt;/a&gt;. You can pickpocket him, kill him, or pay the man to receive the documents. Beyond bringing them to Edwin, there is no other purpose for this item."}
