{"id": "41690", "revid": "47673695", "url": "https://baldursgate.fandom.com/wiki?curid=41690", "title": "Ettin Ghost", "text": "The Ettin Ghost is the &lt;a href=\"ghost\"&gt;ghost&lt;/a&gt; of an &lt;a href=\"ettin\"&gt;ettin&lt;/a&gt; who was killed in the tunnels beneath &lt;a href=\"Dragonspear%20Castle\"&gt;Dragonspear Castle&lt;/a&gt; during the last Dragonspear War. He has remained haunting the &lt;a href=\"Underground%20River\"&gt;Underground River&lt;/a&gt; ever since, and can be found in the extreme west, to the southwest of the Crusader guard fireplace that lies south of the entrance to &lt;a href=\"The%20Warrens\"&gt;The Warrens&lt;/a&gt;.\nWhen &lt;a href=\"Gorion%27s%20Ward\"&gt;Gorion's Ward&lt;/a&gt; stumbles across him, they can either simply fight the Ettin Ghost to receive 4,000 EXP and the &lt;a href=\"Cloak%20of%20the%20Strange%20Beast\"&gt;Cloak of the Strange Beast&lt;/a&gt;, or attempt to talk to him. If they talk, he will explain that he is haunting these caves looking for his lost &lt;a href=\"Ettin%20Club\"&gt;Ettin Club&lt;/a&gt;. Gorion's Ward can now locate the aforementioned club in the &lt;a href=\"Ettin%20Ghost%20Cave\"&gt;Ettin Ghost Cave&lt;/a&gt;, which lies in roughly the central area of the map, on the north side of the river. If given back his club, the grateful Ettin Ghost gives the party the &lt;a href=\"Cloak%20of%20the%20Strange%20Beast\"&gt;Cloak of the Strange Beast&lt;/a&gt; (which he was using as a loincloth, to the evident disgust of Gorion's Ward) and leaves. This grants the party 3,000 EXP.\nNote: The presence of &lt;a href=\"M%27Khiin%20Grubdoubler\"&gt;M'Khiin Grubdoubler&lt;/a&gt; or a &lt;a href=\"Shaman\"&gt;Shaman&lt;/a&gt;-classed &lt;a href=\"Gorion%27s%20Ward\"&gt;Gorion's Ward&lt;/a&gt; may be required in order to communicate with the Ettin Ghost instead of simply fighting with him!"}
{"id": "41775", "revid": "773742", "url": "https://baldursgate.fandom.com/wiki?curid=41775", "title": "Ettin Ghost Cave", "text": "The Ettin Ghost Cave is an that may be discovered in \"\".\nLayout.\nIt is a small sub-area of the &lt;a href=\"Underground%20River\"&gt;Underground River&lt;/a&gt;, containing the remains of an &lt;a href=\"ettin\"&gt;ettin&lt;/a&gt; and a band of adventurers who perished here during the last Dragonspear War. The ghosts of the adventurers still haunt the place, whilst the &lt;a href=\"Ettin%20Ghost\"&gt;Ettin Ghost&lt;/a&gt; has strayed out into the caverns beyond."}
{"id": "36221", "revid": "47673695", "url": "https://baldursgate.fandom.com/wiki?curid=36221", "title": "Ettin Skin Scroll", "text": "The Ettin Skin Scroll, &lt;a href=\"Wyrm%20Tooth\"&gt;Wyrm Tooth&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=\"Carrion%20Crawler%20Egg\"&gt;Carrion Crawler Egg&lt;/a&gt; are given as a reward from &lt;a href=\"Brodle\"&gt;Brodle&lt;/a&gt;. These three items, a &lt;a href=\"Mirror%20Shard\"&gt;Mirror Shard&lt;/a&gt; from &lt;a href=\"Bannor\"&gt;Bannor&lt;/a&gt;'s room and 12,000 gold are needed for &lt;a href=\"Dulf%20Ebonbeard\"&gt;Dulf Ebonbeard&lt;/a&gt; to create... something. I think some part of these quests involves someone named &lt;a href=\"Gezzthemin\"&gt;Gezzthemin&lt;/a&gt;?\n==Description="}
