{"id": "50594", "revid": "35642161", "url": "https://baldursgate.fandom.com/wiki?curid=50594", "title": "Fade NPC walkthrough", "text": "The \"&lt;a href=\"Fade%20NPC\"&gt;Fade NPC&lt;/a&gt;\" mod by \"Mistress Elysia\" adds Fade, a &lt;a href=\"Chaotic%20Neutral\"&gt;chaotic-neutral&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=\"w%3Ac%3Aforgottenrealms%3AFey%27ri\"&gt;fey'ri&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=\"thief\"&gt;thief&lt;/a&gt;, to &lt;a href=\"Baldur%27s%20Gate%20II\"&gt;BG2&lt;/a&gt; as a &lt;a href=\"Companions\"&gt;joinable NPC&lt;/a&gt;.\nShe has a few personal quests.&lt;br&gt;\nThis is a walkthrough for that quest content.&lt;br&gt;\nSPOILER WARNING!\nHow to get her to join.\nStart &lt;a href=\"Baldur%27s%20Gate%20II%20Chapter%203\"&gt;\"Shadows of Amn\" chapter 3&lt;/a&gt; by siding with the &lt;a href=\"Shadow%20Thieves\"&gt;Shadow Thieves&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;br&gt;\nIn your first conversation with &lt;a href=\"Aran%20Linvail\"&gt;Aran Linvail&lt;/a&gt; in &lt;a href=\"Aran%20Linvail%27s%20Hideout\"&gt;his hideout&lt;/a&gt;, he introduces you to Fade, who stands behind him. Talk to her afterwards to let her join your party.\nRomance.\nMuch of Fade's quest content requires that you are romancing her, so a few words about that.\nFade romances any male protagonist who is not already in another committed romance.\nFade generally initiates romance talks in intervals of 45+ minutes of real time \u2013 although the talks will be delayed if you are indoors/underground, or in combat, or Fade or the protagonist are incapacitated, etc.&lt;br&gt;\nAt certain points, you have to &lt;a href=\"rest\"&gt;rest&lt;/a&gt; the party in order for the romance to continue.\nNormal romance talks, which occur strictly in this order:\n\"Bonus\" romance talks, which can happen at specific points in the game:\nNormal romance talks, which occur strictly in this order:\n\"Bonus\" romance talks, which can happen at specific points in the game:\nThere are also player-initiated talks: Besides flirting etc., you can ask he